episodes.title: American Greed: The Polygamist & The Bio Fuel Baron | CNBC Prime
episodes.description:
Watch the first 10 minutes of the season premiere of American Greed called “The Polygamist & The Bio Fuel Baron” exclusively here on our YouTube channel. This episode about the polygamist Jacob Kingston and the man known as The Lion premieres on Tuesday, September 27 at 10pm ET on CNBC.
